rows.label: fev01_110_125_msg0001
rows.name:
Now that I've got Gramps to agree,
I need to get everything ready.

rows.label: fev01_110_125_msg0002
rows.name:
Having 100,000 G really gets
the imagination going...

rows.label: fev01_110_125_msg0003
rows.name:
I could get a brand new salvager
suit, the whole setup...

rows.label: fev01_110_125_msg0004
rows.name:
No, I can't do that... I need
to be frugal. Or there won't be
enough to send back home...

rows.label: fev01_110_125_msg0005
rows.name:
Right, no major expenses
for now. First stop will
be Kirakira Accessories.

rows.label: fev01_110_125_msg0006
rows.name:
Better safe than sorry. I might
have to battle another Crustip
like the one from my last job.
